## 0.5 NEW bugs discovered during the fix (not yet fixed)
- [x] FIXED 2026-07-22: `workers/billing-sync.ts` (5Г—) + `workers/email-send.ts` (1Г—) audit_log
      INSERTs used a nonexistent `metadata` column в†’ remapped to `new_data` (schema-correct)
- [x] FIXED 2026-07-22: `generate-monthly` (route + rent-generate worker) вЂ” confirmed the
      `ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING` matched NO constraint (only UNIQUE was idempotency_key = NULL)
      в†’ re-runs would duplicate every student's rent. Added migration 008
      (`uq_payments_student_month` partial unique index), explicit conflict targets,
      pre-check that skips already-billed students WITHOUT burning receipt numbers,
