## 1.5 NEW schema/code gaps discovered while building (not yet fixed)
- [ ] **CNIC stored PLAINTEXT** in `cnic_encrypted` (students POST + import) вЂ” needs an
      encryption service (AES-256-GCM like auth.ts TOTP) + backfill migration; reveal-cnic
      currently returns the raw stored value
- [ ] `auth.ts` SELECTs `display_name, theme, language, totp_secret_enc, totp_backup_codes`
      from users вЂ” NONE of these columns exist in migration 001 (auth would fail at runtime);
      needs a migration or code alignment
- [ ] Spec's warden permission flags (`can_edit`, `can_delete`, `can_settings`) not in users
      schema вЂ” spec DELETE /students gating can't be implemented until added
- [ ] Spec's hostel settings fields (`tagline`, `brandColor`, `showBranding`,
      `autoMonthAdvance`) not in hostels schema
- [ ] students.ts pre-existing routes lack JSON-Schema validation (hand-rolled checks only)
      and use role 'super_admin' which isn't in the users role CHECK

